Food is professionally prepared and the staff members are helpful and polite. My favourite is the done to order shrimp pasta salad, its is simply an experience everyone deserves to have. Don't be afraid to throw in a smoothy with your order and add some popping pearls.

Honestly there's nothing special about the food here. Presentation is okay but the food is just subpar i had the goat and the jerk chicken. The goat was flooded in gravy more bone than actual meat and the Jerk chicken had little flavor mixed with the burnt skin.
